timelineItems.text: ¡GOOOL! (75') | FABIÁN CASTILLO Gran combinación de @FCDallas y el colombiano la clava al segundo palo en el contragolpe. #DALvRSL 2-0

timelineItems.comment: Attempt missed. Robbie Findley (Real Salt Lake) left footed shot from outside the box is high and wide to the left. Assisted by Kyle Beckerman.

timelineItems.comment: Attempt missed. Joao Plata (Real Salt Lake) right footed shot from outside the box is close, but misses the top right corner. Assisted by Kyle Beckerman.

timelineItems.text: How many missed efforts and bobbled touches before #RSL realize findley is not worth the money we pay.

timelineItems.text: This #RSL game is very frustrating to watch. Up a man, dominating the time of poss, and so many missed chances.

timelineItems.comment: Attempt missed. Joao Plata (Real Salt Lake) left footed shot from a difficult angle on the left is close, but misses to the left. Assisted by Luis Gil with a cross.

timelineItems.name: Andy Edwards
timelineItems.text: #FCDallas—about to go to 10 games unbeaten—will lose to 9th-in-the-East Chicago next week. Because this is #MLS, and don't you forget it.

timelineItems.name: ImaginaryTurboFriend
timelineItems.text: In the brief time #rsl was pushing for tie, Zach Lloyd made man tackles. Stout. #opta

timelineItems.name: Major League Soccer
timelineItems.text: You can't stop Fabian Castillo. You can only hope to contain him. Even then... http://t.co/NX72KJNcSl #DALvRSL

timelineItems.name: Chad Kunde
timelineItems.text: #RSL's passing has slowed down after the sending-off. That's opposite of what's going to win the match against a short side.

timelineItems.comment: Attempt missed. Ned Grabavoy (Real Salt Lake) left footed shot from outside the box is close, but misses the top left corner. Assisted by Luis Gil.

timelineItems.name: Kali K.
timelineItems.text: #RSL just not good enough tonight. Completely off in the final third and some mental lapses.

timelineItems.name: Travis Cain
timelineItems.text: #RSL to work on finishing at the next practice?

timelineItems.name: Brian
timelineItems.text: #RSL just doesn't look sharp. So sloppy, soooo many shanks.

timelineItems.name: Charles Barnard
timelineItems.text: Only stat you need to know tonight. #RSL is now scoring a goal every 137 min. when Findley is on the field. Every 52 min w/o him #RSLStats

Ned Grabavoy (Real Salt Lake) wins a free kick in the attacking half.

timelineItems.name: Kacy Hill
timelineItems.text: Is it just me or is @KyleBeckerman already on fire tonight?! He's always on....but he seems just insanely on point tonight! #KB5 #RSL #3PTS

timelineItems.desc: Goal!  FC Dallas 2, Real Salt Lake 1. Olmes Garcia (Real Salt Lake) right footed shot from the center of the box to the bottom left corner.
timelineItems.title: GOAL: Olmes Garcia's bicycle kick sneaks in

timelineItems.name: Fútbol MLS
timelineItems.text: No tiene sentido intentar detener a Fabián Castillo en este momento. No hay forma. Dejen así: http://t.co/wFDmTYTP4a #DALvRSL

timelineItems.text: Easiest thing for #RSL to do tonight is blame this debacle on Velasquez's hair. That'll put anyone off. @MLS #deadraccoon #davycrockett

timelineItems.comment: Corner,  Real Salt Lake. Conceded by Je-Vaughn Watson.

timelineItems.name: Steve Rossen
timelineItems.text: Going to make this last 2 minutes a little tense. #FCDallas

timelineItems.name: Robert Trishman
timelineItems.text: Why do I feel like that goal is huge for the season even if #RSL loses?

timelineItems.name: Major League Soccer
timelineItems.text: Garcia rides the bike. Gets one back for @RealSaltLake in stoppage time. #DALvRSL

timelineItems.text: Olmes-Garcia with the bicycle kick goal. Took a deflection on the shot but still a pretty effort. Likely too little, too late for #RSL
